rComments: Everyone boosted him so much and he is just another prof. Yeah he is decent but no way is he the best prof around.

Mike is awesome. He's succinct and crystal clear. He's funny and he's tall. He's smart and he's nice. I like how he knows the stuff he knows. I feel like I am smarter just for being in the room with him, but not because of a relative thing. More like his intelligence leaks osmotically into my skull. I hope to grow up to be Mike one day.
The best prof I've had. Clear, Knows the material, helpful, smart.

Mike is the most genuinely supportive and clear-headed prof I've had to date at U of T. Love the practice problems he gives you time to do in class, they're amazing prep for the midterm/final - there's a reason his students consistently outperform all other sections.
Best prof ive come across at the Rotman school of commerce..
